text: KNLF (95.9 FM) is a radio station broadcasting a Contemporary Christian format. Licensed to Quincy and serving the surrounding Sierra Nevada area. It is in Plumas County, Northern California. The station is currently owned by New Life Broadcasting. The stations airs AFR on Monday-Friday at 12:30pm-2pm, 3pm-5pm, and 5:30pm. ==External links== * * * NLF Category:Contemporary Christian radio stations in the United States Category:Plumas County, California Category:American Family Radio stations NLF
